A solitary figure in a white lab coat stands before an enormous wall covered in interconnected constellation maps, mathematical equations, and intricate diagrams, their back to the viewer as they contemplate the patterns. The scene is rendered in warm, soft watercolors with gentle earth tones and muted blues characteristic of Studio Ghibli animation. Dust motes float in golden afternoon light streaming through tall arched windows. The room resembles an old observatory library with curved wooden bookshelves reaching toward a domed ceiling. Small potted plants sit on windowsills, and scattered papers with sketches cover a worn wooden desk nearby. The atmosphere conveys quiet intellectual curiosity and the beauty of deep, solitary contemplation.
